21
00:02:02,067 --> 00:02:04,520
(Tai's Detective Agency)

22
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,800
Did you see it clear?

23
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,600
This is Tai's Detective Agency.

24
